thread.title: TUT to release final SRC election results

author: news24.com
title: TUT to release final SRC election results
text:
Pretoria - The Tshwane University of Technology (TUT) is expected to release the final results of its Student Representative Council (SRC) elections on Tuesday morning.
"The provisional results were released to students. They have 24 hours to lodge any issues in writing to the chief electoral commissioner," spokesperson Willa de Ruyter told News24.
"The final results will be released... [on Tuesday] morning."
Economic Freedom Fighters members and rival organisations clashed at the TUT Pretoria West campus on Thursday ahead of the SRC elections.
